  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an extension study designed to assess the safety and durability of platelet count
      increases with romiplostim treatment of thrombocytopenic subjects with Immune (Idiopathic)
      Thrombocytopenia Purpura. This study is available to pediatric subjects who have completed a
      previous romiplostim ITP study and meet the eligibility criteria of this study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
